# CiscoTest
Api's are created using PYTHON.

Install Python.

pip install flask

pip install flask-restful

pip install numpy

#steps to run

python ciscoService.py

...making requests

curl http://localhost:5000/deck -d "task=deck1" -X POST -v (to create a new DECK)
curl http://localhost:5000/deck/deck1 (GET a named deck in its current order).
curl http://localhost:5000/deck (GET a list of decks).
 curl http://localhost:5000/deck/deck2 -X PUT -v  (PUT to shuffle an existing deck deck2).
curl http://localhost:5000/deck/deck1(DELETE an existing deck deck1)


